// CLIENT RESULTS ☁️
for the beautiful @houseofartistry__

in just 3 months we've seen a huge uplift across the board in followers, reach, engagement & of course traffic to the website

we started at 18,000 views per month and are now sitting at 400,000+ 🪽

not by accident, our strategy has combined high & low intensity content to strategically reach new eyeballs and keep them highly engaged with the page 

we prioritise fresh, unique content in their niche to inspire clients & fellow industry peers, positioning them as a leader in their space in more ways than one //

to top it all off, they're the most beautiful team and an absolute dream to work with 🤍 

is your brand next? july applications are now open, comment SOCIAL for more info 💙
